divs: Sighting DetailsThe witness called to report that she, her husband and 24-year old son had witnessed a starlike object which looked like a boomerang or rounded triangle through binoculars.It was accompanied by 6 to 10 smaller, objects. An airplane flew underneath where the object was seen. The witness began to feel that she was being watched and went inside the house. She has seen objects similar to this two times previously in roughly the same spot. Several years ago on State Road 84 a low dark shape flew over their car.
